<i>adverb</i>: 착실히 [착씰히], 열심히 [열씸히], 부지런히 [부지런히], 근실히 [근ː실히], 근면히 [근ː면히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>착실히 [착씰히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. diligently</dd><br>
<dd>한결같이 올바르고 성실하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being upright and consistent in doing something.</dd><br>
<dd>2. sufficiently</dd><br>
<dd>일정한 기준이나 정도에 모자람 없이 충분하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being adequate in level or amount without lacking.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>열심히 [열씸히]</dt><br>
<dd>hard; diligently; zealously</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일에 온 정성을 다하여.</dd><br>
<dd>With all one's heart.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>부지런히 [부지런히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. diligently</dd><br>
<dd>게으름을 부리지 않고 꾸준하게 열심히.</dd><br>
<dd>In an attitude of working steadily without being idle.</dd><br>
<dd>2. hurriedly</dd><br>
<dd>빠르게 서둘러서.</dd><br>
<dd>Quickly, in a hurry.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>근실히 [근ː실히]</dt><br>
<dd>sincerely; diligently</dd><br>
<dd>부지런하고 진실하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a diligent and truthful manner.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>근면히 [근ː면히]</dt><br>
<dd>diligently; earnestly</dd><br>
<dd>성실하고 부지런하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a sincere and industrious manner.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>